short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Restore a crumb of dignity to our national broadcaster.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ABC News articles often have multiple headlines: an ordinary one and a clickbait one. This extension replaces the clickbait headline with the ordinary one on most pages.
